oad-alt=""> <img id="m4722" class="module image" src="/uploads/lFTO44FF/495x0_480x0/imageedit_9_3440041087_116.png" alt="" width="495" height="124" data-author="" fetchpriority="high"/> </noscript> </a> <div id="m3014" class="module text"><p class="custom4" style="text-align: center;">Quality Bathrooms without Splashing out!</p></div> <a data-global="phone"  id="m1727" class="module button2 hidden-lg hidden-md" href="tel:01373454245"  title="" role="button" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="phone_link"> <span class="buttonLabel labelRight">Tap to Call</span> </a> </div> <div class="col col col-lg-6 col-md-7 col-sm-9 flexCol"><div id="m1805" class="module autospacer"></div> <div class="flexWrap"> <div id="m4133" class="module text hidden-sm"><p class="smallsubtitle">Call <span data-global="phone">01373 454245</span> for More Details about Our Bathroom Suites</p><p class="smallsubtitle"><span class="iconfont"></span>&nbsp;07866 787662<br></p><p class="smallsubtitle"><span class="iconfont"></span>&nbsp;<a href="mailto:robbo2@btconnect.com" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="email_link">robbo2@btconnect.com</a><br></p></div> </div> <div id="m1848" class="module autospacer"></div> <div class="flexWrap"> <ul id="m2656" class="module socialmedia"> <li class=" "> <a class="" href="https://www.facebook.com/bathroomwarehousefrome/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="Facebook" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="social_link" aria-label="facebook"> <span class="fa fa-facebook" aria-hidden="true"></span> </a> </li> </ul></div> </div> </div> </div> <div id="r1059" class="row "> <div class="container container-fluid "><div id="c3637" class="col col-sm-12"><nav id="m5000" class="module nav" data-settings="vertical=false,direction=right,push=true,activeParent=false" aria-label="Navigation" tabindex="-1"> <ul class="navContainer"><li class=" active"> <a href="/" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Home</a> </li><li class=""> <a href="/gallery" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Gallery</a> </li><li class=""> <a href="/about-us" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">About Us</a> </li><li class=""> <a href="/contact" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Contact</a> </li><li class=" hidden-lg hidden-md hidden-sm"> <a href="/terms-and-conditions" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Terms and Conditions</a> </li><li class=" hidden-lg hidden-md hidden-sm"> <a href="/privacy-policy" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Privacy Policy</a> </li></ul> </nav></div> </div> </div> </header><div id="r5002" role="main" class="row designRow"> <div class="container container-fixed"><div class="col col-sm-12"><div id="r1348" class="row "> <div class="container container-fixed "><div id="c2536" class="col col-sm-12"></div> </div> </div> <div id="r5663" class="row " data-req="rowgroup" data-rowgroupsettings="transition=slowFadeIn,auto=true,dots=true"> <div class="container container-fluid"></div> </div> <div id="r4610" class="row "> <div class="container container-fixed "><div class="col col-sm-12"><div id="m2448" class="module text"><p class="smallsubtitle" style="text-align: center;">BROWSE OUR GALLERY</p></div> <a id="m1248" class="module button" href="/gallery"  title="" role="button" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked"> <span class="buttonLabel labelRight">GALLERY</span> </a></div> </div> </div> <div id="r4669" class="row "> <div class="container container-fixed "><div id="c3314" class="col col-lg-7 col-sm-12 col-md-12"><div id="m4051" class="module text"><h1 style="text-align: center;" class="subtitle">A Family-Run Business You Can Trust</h1><p class="bodytext" style="text-align: center;">Bathroom Warehouse has built an impeccable reputation for bespoke bathrooms that meet your exact needs. Whether you simply want a few taps changing or desire a brand-new and luxurious suite, our experienced team have the skills required to expertly transform your old, fatigued bathroom into a place of beauty and indulgence.</p></div> </div> <div id="c3614" class="col col-lg-5 col-sm-12 col-md-12 flexCol"><div id="m4854" class="module autospacer"></div> <div class="flexWrap"> <div id="m2041" class="module text"><p class="subtitle" style="text-align: center;"><a href="/contact" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Contact&nbsp;our bathroom company in Frome, Somerset, for a variety of fitted bathrooms.</a></p></div> </div> <div id="m3443" class="module autospacer"></div> </div> </div> </div> <div id="r1104" class="row "> <div class="container container-fixed "><div id="c1833" class="col col-sm-12"><div id="m2166" class="module gallery" data-req="gallery,lightbox" data-settings="imagecols=4,imagecols-md=4,margin=2,margin-md=2,margin-sm=6,dontcrop=true,gallerycaptioninpopup=true,imagenr-sm=1,auto=true,transition-sm=slowFadeIn" data-before-text="Before" data-after-text="After" role="region" aria-label="Slides"> <div class="slides" aria-live="polite"> <div class="slide"> <ul class="pics clear"> <li> <a href="/uploads/hBwDR3TP/767x0_2560x0/image002.jpg" title="" aria-label="Image travistock, Opens dialog" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked"> <span class="thumb"> <span class="thumbInner"> <img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAAC0lEQVQYV2NgAAIAAAUAAarVyFEAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="travistock" width="272" height="129" data-author="" data-ai=""/> <noscript data-lazyload-src="/uploads/hBwDR3TP/736x0_283x0/image002.jpg" data-lazyload-alt="travistock"> <img src="/uploads/hBwDR3TP/736x0_283x0/image002.jpg" alt="travistock" width="272" height="129" data-author="" data-ai=""> </noscript> </span> </span> <span class="bodytext caption"></span> </a> </li> <li> <a href="/uploads/y16Jmhu1/767x0_2560x0/image003.jpg" title="" aria-label="Image roper rhodes, Opens dialog" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked"> <span class="thumb"> <span class="thumbInner"> <img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAAC0lEQVQYV2NgAAIAAAUAAarVyFEAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="roper rhodes" width="343" height="122" data-author="" data-ai=""/> <noscript data-lazyload-src="/uploads/y16Jmhu1/736x0_283x0/image003.jpg" data-lazyload-alt="roper rhodes"> <img src="/uploads/y16Jmhu1/736x0_283x0/image003.jpg" alt="roper rhodes" width="343" height="122" data-author="" data-ai=""> </noscript> </span> </span> <span class="bodytext caption"></span> </a> </li> <li> <a href="/uploads/ArNSsguv/767x0_2560x0/image005.jpg" title="" aria-label="Image lakes, Opens dialog" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked"> <span class="thumb"> <span class="thumbInner"> <img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAAC0lEQVQYV2NgAAIAAAUAAarVyFEAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="lakes" width="378" height="200" data-author="" data-ai=""/> <noscript data-lazyload-src="/uploads/ArNSsguv/736x0_283x0/image005.jpg" data-lazyload-alt="lakes"> <img src="/uploads/ArNSsguv/736x0_283x0/image005.jpg" alt="lakes" width="378" height="200" data-author="" data-ai=""> </noscript> </span> </span> <span class="bodytext caption"></span> </a> </li> <li> <a href="/uploads/m2r3D5tX/767x0_2560x0/image006.jpg" title="" aria-label="Image multi panel, Opens dialog" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked"> <span class="thumb"> <span class="thumbInner"> <img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAAC0lEQVQYV2NgAAIAAAUAAarVyFEAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="multi panel" width="410" height="300" data-author="" data-ai=""/> <noscript data-lazyload-src="/uploads/m2r3D5tX/736x0_283x0/image006.jpg" data-lazyload-alt="multi panel"> <img src="/uploads/m2r3D5tX/736x0_283x0/image006.jpg" alt="multi panel" width="410" height="300" data-author="" data-ai=""> </noscript> </span> </span> <span class="bodytext caption"></span> </a> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div></div> </div> </div> <div id="r4055" class="row "> <div class="container container-fluid "><div id="c1161" class="col col-sm-12"><div id="m1828" class="module text"><h2 class="subtitle" style="text-align: center;">About Us</h2><p class="bodytext" style="text-align: center;">Our highly regarded bathroom company in Frome, Somerset, gives you the chance to obtain the place of luxury you’ve always dreamed of. Established in 2005, the bathroom specialists from our business remove your bathroom for your convenience and effortlessly install your new suite for you. You can mix and match various fitted bathrooms with any features you like while arranging your own fitting if you don’t require an installation from our reputable company.&nbsp;</p><p class="bodytext" style="text-align: center;"><br>Priding ourselves on offering quality work at all times, we cater to individual budgets with our highly competitive prices. Free parking is directly available just outside of our showroom, so make sure you pop in to see us to discover your ideal bathroom.</p></div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <footer><div id="r1074" class="row "> <div class="container container-fixed "><div id="c3869" class="col col-sm-12 col-lg-3 col-md-12"><a href="/"  title="" aria-label="" class="imageModuleWrap" id="w_m1581" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked"> <img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAAC0lEQVQYV2NgAAIAAAUAAarVyFEAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="" data-author="" width="495" height="124" fetchpriority="high"/> <noscript data-lazyload-src="/uploads/lFTO44FF/495x0_320x0/imageedit_9_3440041087_116.png" data-lazyload-id="m1581" data-lazyload-class="module image" data-lazyload-alt="" data-req="" data-settings="enablehover=false,showelement=,hovertransition="> <img id="m1581" class="module image" src="/uploads/lFTO44FF/495x0_320x0/imageedit_9_3440041087_116.png" alt="" width="495" height="124" data-author="" fetchpriority="high"/> </noscript> </a> <div id="m1666" class="module text"><p class="footertext" style="text-align: center;"><a href="/privacy-policy" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Privacy Policy</a></p></div> <div id="m4238" class="module text"><p class="footertext" style="text-align: center;"><a href="/terms-and-conditions" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Terms and Conditions</a></p></div> </div> <div id="c2452" class="col col-sm-12 col-lg-3 col-md-4"><div id="m4120" class="module text"><p class="footertext">Unit 2, Whitworth Road<br>Marston Trading Estate<br>Frome,&nbsp;Somerset <br>BA11 4BY</p></div> </div> <div id="c2343" class="col col-sm-12 col-lg-3 col-md-4"><div id="m3259" class="module text hidden-sm"><p class="footertext" style="text-align: center;">Phone:&nbsp;<span data-global="phone">01373 454245</span><br>Mobile:&nbsp;07866 787662<br>Email:&nbsp;<a href="mailto:robbo2@btconnect.com" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="email_link">robbo2@btconnect.com</a></p></div> <ul id="m4858" class="module socialmedia"> <li class=" "> <a class="" href="https://www.facebook.com/bathroomwarehousefrome/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="Facebook" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="social_link" aria-label="facebook"> <span class="fa fa-facebook" aria-hidden="true"></span> </a> </li> </ul><div id="m2045" class="module text hidden-lg hidden-md"><p class="footertext">Phone: <a data-global="phone"  href="tel:01373454245" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="phone_link">01373 454245</a><br>Mobile: <a href="tel:07866 787662" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="phone_link">07866 787662</a><br>Email: <a href="mailto:robbo2@btconnect.com" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="email_link">robbo2@btconnect.com</a></p></div> </div> <div id="c2800" class="col col-sm-12 col-lg-3 col-md-4"><div id="m2274" class="module text"><p class="footertext" style="text-align: center;">Business Hours: <br>Monday - Friday,&nbsp;9:00 a.m. – 5:00 p.m.&nbsp;<br>Saturday, 9:00 a.m. – 1:00 p.m.</p></div> </div> </div> </div> <div id="r2945" class="row "> <div class="container container-fixed "><div class="col col-sm-12"><div id="m2509" class="module text"><p class="footertext" style="text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span></span>Serving, &nbsp;Frome, Warminster, Westbury, Trowbridge, Shepton Mallet, Radstock, Wincanton, and Any Surrounding Areas</p></div> </div> </div> </div> </footer> <div class="row brandfooter noPadding"> <div class="container container-fixed"> <div class="col col-md-12 col-lg-12 col-sm-12 brandLogoContainer" style="text-align: center; line-height: 40px"> <span class="brandText"> © 2025. Website designed and built by <a href="https://local.reachsolutions.co.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="link_clicked">Reach Solutions</a> </span> </div> </div> </div></div> </div> </div> <script async data-cookieconsent="ignore" nomodule src="https://site-assets.cdnmns.com/afa8b3e41591ac4ba7ed4283ce484259/js/loader-polyfills.js?1776164602665"></script><script async data-cookieconsent="ignore" src="https://site-assets.cdnmns.com/afa8b3e41591ac4ba7ed4283ce484259/js/loader.js?1776164602665"></script><script type='application/ld+json'>{"@context":"http://schema.org","@type":"LocalBusiness","@id":"https://www.bathroomsfrome.co.uk/#global_business","name":"Bathroom Warehouse","address":{"@type":"PostalAddress","streetAddress":"Unit 2, Whitworth Road, Marston Trading Estate","addressLocality":"Frome","addressRegion":"Somerset","postalCode":"BA11 4BY","addressCountry":""},"email":"robbo2@btconnect.com","telephone":"01373 454245","url":"https://www.bathroomsfrome.co.uk"}</script><!-- Cookiebot: Google consent mode v2 defaults --> <script type='text/javascript' data-cookieconsent='ig